2026-05-06 06:50:08,460 [INFO] [gemini] - **Performance Optimization**: Split the React contexts (`DocumentContext` and `UIContext`) into separate **State** and **Dispatch** contexts. This allows high-frequency UI components to consume only the dispatch function, preventing unnecessary re-renders when the state changes.
2026-05-06 06:50:08,730 [INFO] [gemini] - **Component Efficiency**: Memoized critical canvas components (`ObjectRenderer` and `DrawingLayer`) using `React.memo`. They now receive only the necessary state values as props, further reducing render cycles.
2026-05-06 06:50:08,730 [INFO] [gemini] - **Architectural Cleanup**:
2026-05-06 06:50:08,996 [INFO] [gemini]     - Decomposed the massive `Toolbar.tsx` into three manageable sub-components: `ObjectPropertyEditor`, `ZoomControls`, and `ProjectActions`.
2026-05-06 06:50:09,128 [INFO] [gemini]     - Centralized magic numbers and default dimensions into `client/src/core/constants.ts`.
2026-05-06 06:50:09,129 [INFO] [gemini]     - Removed the deprecated `useEditor` hook.
